casebody.data:
No. 156,

Misc.

Kennedy v. Commandant, United States Disciplinary Barracks, Fort Leavenworth. Solicitor General Marshall, Assistant Attorney General Vinson and Beatrice Rosenberg for respondent in opposition.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of habeas corpus and other relief denied.

Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion.
